Scene - [Click to show/hide] <p>This Custom Format will try to recognize so-called "scene releases". Depending on your preferences, you can give it a negative score <code>-10000</code>, a positive score, or just skip adding it altogether.</p> JSON - [Click to show/hide] <pre><code>{
